high_descs: Head around and turn left to the sofa.
Pick the spatula from the couch.
Walk towards and turn left to the bathroom.
Go the stairs and turn in to left and put the spatula inside the sink.
Rinse it well and turn right and turn right to the sidetable.
Turn right and place the spatula on the corner of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: To place the spatula at the corner of the SideTable.

high_descs: Walk to the living room and go next to the sofa.
Pick up the spatula that is on the sofa.
Take the spatula and go into the bathroom and stand in front of the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink and wash it.
Remove it and take it to the bedroom.
Put it down on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Removing Spatula and placing it on the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the grey sofa.
Pick up the spatula from the couch.
Turn around and head right to enter the bathroom on the left.
Wash the spatula in the sink and take it out.
Turn left to exit the room and turn right to walk past the sidetable and walk into the bedroom to reach the nightstand next to the bed.
Place the spatula on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed spatula on the side table.
